---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import TransformCTA from '../../components/TransformCTA.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Botox - Renasci Medical Spa"
  description="Tratamientos de Botox para suavizar líneas de expresión y arrugas dinámicas con resultados naturales y duraderos. Agenda tu cita en Renasci Medical Spa."
>
  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center text-center overflow-hidden">
    <img 
      src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1612349317150-e413f6a5b16d?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3"
      alt="Botox treatment"
      class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
      loading="eager"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/45"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/30 to-pink-500/30 backdrop-blur-sm text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-6 border border-white/30">
        Tratamientos Faciales
      </div>
      <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-4xl md:text-6xl text-white mb-6">Botox</h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/90 mb-8 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Neuromodulador para relajar selectivamente músculos responsables de líneas dinámicas y arrugas de expresión.
      </p>
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-white/15 to-pink-100/15 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-card mb-8 inline-block border border-white/30">
        <div class="text-sm text-white/80 mb-1">Precio desde</div>
        <div class="font-display font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-pink-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">$350</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-white/80 mt-1">Duración: 30–45 min</div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
        <a href="#detalles" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-pink-500 text-white rounded-2xl font-semibold text-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:opacity-90 hover:-translate-y-[2px] hover:shadow-xl focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-white/50">
          Ver Detalles
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="tel:+13856092840" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-call to-emerald-500 text-white rounded-2xl font-semibold text-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:opacity-90 hover:-translate-y-[2px] hover:shadow-xl focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-call/50" aria-label="Llamar Renasci">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/></svg>
          385 609 2840
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <nav class="bg-background py-6 border-b border-gray-100">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <ol class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
        <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Inicio</a></li>
        <li class="text-gray-400">/</li>
        <li><a href="/services" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Servicios</a></li>
        <li class="text-gray-400">/</li>
        <li class="text-gray-900 font-medium">Botox</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section id="detalles" class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-background">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="relative group">
          <img src="/img/services/Xeomin-botox.jpg.webp" alt="Botox procedure" class="w-full h-[400px] lg:h-[500px] object-cover rounded-3xl shadow-2xl transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-[1.02]" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-50 to-purple-50 rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-10 shadow-xl">
            <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl lg:text-4xl bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-pink-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-6">Botox</h2>
            <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              <p class="mb-4">Tratamiento con neurotoxina botulínica purificada que relaja temporalmente los músculos responsables de arrugas dinámicas.</p>
              <p class="mb-4">Áreas típicas: patas de gallo, frente, entrecejo y otras zonas con contracción repetitiva que generan líneas visibles.</p>
              <p>Resultados seguros y naturales cuando se aplica por profesionales certificados.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <TransformCTA />
</BaseLayout>

